---
title: Chermoula Lentil & Couscous Bowl with Honey Carrots & Lemon Yoghurt Dressing
description: We love the tender texture of lentils and couscous; the fibrous grains and legumes are the perfect pair for handling bold flavours.
Combine that with spiced and roasted veggies, creamy yoghurt and fresh mint for a bowl to remember!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-lentil-couscous-bowl-ba023137.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/chermoula-lentil-couscous-bowl-60bd9f8a05fd87276b2877ff-1af6f63c.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/chermoula-lentil-and-couscous-bowl-60bd9f8a05fd87276b2877ff
cuisine: Middle East
course: main course
